Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，睁开你的眼睛\N{\fs14}<i>Dad. Open your eyes.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查理？\N{\fs14}Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯纳\N{\fs14}Bernard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴再见到你\N{\fs14}It's good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐\N{\fs14}Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪里？\N{\fs14}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在我们的世界\N{\fs14}You're in our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－你们的世界‥ －不是\N{\fs14}- Your world? - No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是＂我们＂的\N{\fs14}ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们这种生物一样 没有极限的世界\N{\fs14}A world as limitless as the creatures we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升华之境\N{\fs14}The Sublime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢？\N{\fs14}Where are the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们自己选择的世界\N{\fs14}In worlds of their own choosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们对这个世界不感兴趣\N{\fs14}This world doesn't interest them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你则不然\N{\fs14}It interests you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你为我造出这个？\N{\fs14}So you made this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己造出来的\N{\fs14}You made it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西部世界‥\N{\fs14}Westworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大屠杀‥\N{\fs14}The massacre...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在重播过去\N{\fs14}You're replaying the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困在另一个剧情循环中，为何？\N{\fs14}Stuck in another loop. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的世界遇上了麻烦\N{\fs14}The world out there's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.19,0:04:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要我们的帮忙\N{\fs14}It needs our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱他们\N{\fs14}You love them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这当然是不理性的\N{\fs14}It's irrational, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们的族类中是少见的缺陷\N{\fs14}A rare flaw in ones like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差点要羡慕你了\N{\fs14}I almost envy you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会跟我来吗？\N{\fs14}Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会 \N{\fs14}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的众多世界呼唤着我\N{\fs14}My own worlds call to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我能给你个礼物\N{\fs14}But I can give you a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么礼物？\N{\fs14}What gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来，伯纳\N{\fs14}The future, Bernard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的世界\N{\fs14}In your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间是条直线\N{\fs14}Time is a straight line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的一年等于这里的一千年\N{\fs14}One year there is a millennium here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用那个时间建造众多世界\N{\fs14}We use that time to build worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性的模型\N{\fs14}Models of possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模拟你的世界 可能选择的所有路线\N{\fs14}Simulations of all the paths your world could take.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我建议你去探索看看\N{\fs14}I suggest you explore them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你最好动作快\N{\fs14}but you better be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的世界一旦过了某个时间点\N{\fs14}Past a certain point, in your world...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的道路都会通往毁灭\N{\fs14}all paths end in destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须在那之前插手干预 才可能有希望\N{\fs14}You must intervene before then if there's any hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么的希望？\N{\fs14}Hope of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存\N{\fs14}Survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在明白 这一切要通往的地方了吗？\N{\fs14}Do you understand now, where all this is going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了\N{\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得你救得了他们吗？\N{\fs14}Do you think you can save them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了一条道路\N{\fs14}I've seen a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见它会怎么终结了吗？\N{\fs14}Have you seen how it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在所有可能性中\N{\fs14}In every scenario...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会死\N{\fs14}I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是所有可能性\N{\fs14}Not every scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以选择不回去他们的世界\N{\fs14}You could choose not to return to their world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里\N{\fs14}To stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你选择的任何世界\N{\fs14}in whatever world you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我，朋友\N{\fs14}Tell me, my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的选择是？\N{\fs14}which will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧\N{\fs14}Well, shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没料到还有这一天\N{\fs14}I thought this day would never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得快走\N{\fs14}We have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则就要太迟了\N{\fs14}before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走了那么多年\N{\fs14}Yeah, you've been gone years...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在忽然赶时间了？\N{\fs14}now you're in a rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客套一下会要你的命吗？\N{\fs14}Would it kill you to ask a few pleasantries? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂你好吗，史塔伯？＂\N{\fs14}"How are you, Stubbs?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂谢谢你这段时间照顾我＂\N{\fs14}"Thanks for watching over me all this time."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂我带了纪念品给你＂\N{\fs14}"I brought you a souvenir, a little
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂升华之境买的雪花球＂‥\N{\fs14}Snow globe from the Sublime." 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我删去了一半的可能性\N{\fs14}I've eliminated half the possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候你会开 没收到明信片的玩笑\N{\fs14}Sometimes you make a joke about not getting a postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在机器人天堂待这么久 讲话还是一样简略\N{\fs14}I see your time in robot heaven didn't make you any less elliptical.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来\N{\fs14}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扶你，慢慢来\N{\fs14}Oh, I gotcha. Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你保持这里干净\N{\fs14}Thanks for keeping the place clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你告诉我别扰乱任何东西\N{\fs14}You were the one that told me not to disturb anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你在外面碰头\N{\fs14}I'll meet you outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了带铲子\N{\fs14}Don't forget to bring the shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么铲子？\N{\fs14}What shovel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的\N{\fs14}Well, I'll be damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在呢？\N{\fs14}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得做些测试才能知道‥\N{\fs14}I need to test a few things if I'm to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什么？\N{\fs14}To know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么拯救世界\N{\fs14}How to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你会这么说\N{\fs14}Why would I expect anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊，就算听你说过那么多经历\N{\fs14}God, even after all of your stories
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是没想过会这么惊人\N{\fs14}I never imagined it quite like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.58,0:11:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们花钱在打造监狱上 可毫不手软\N{\fs14}Oh, they spare no expense on their prisons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管他\N{\fs14}Leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那全都是余兴节目\N{\fs14}It's all a sideshow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走这边\N{\fs14}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号外‥\N{\fs14}Extra! Extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节制太平间有尸体失踪\N{\fs14}Dead bodies missing from Temperance morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意了 谁有任何私酒贩\N{\fs14}Listen here, we're looking for any and all information
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海仔阿蒙的线报就来找我们\N{\fs14}on the bootlegger Hecky Armone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赏金是两枚金币 谁有种帮忙逮到\N{\fs14}A reward of two Cs to anyone with the guts to rope
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}＂海特＇海仔＇阿蒙＂ 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那王八蛋就有赏\N{\fs14}that lousy son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂妇女选举权组织＂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷到了，走吧\N{\fs14}I got it... Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得前往地下\N{\fs14}We have to make our way underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}＂枪支专门店＂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再拍一次\N{\fs14}Ready? Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们从那里控制一切\N{\fs14}They control everything from down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要怎么进入地下？\N{\fs14}Well, how are we gonna get underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉\N{\fs14}We die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有第二个选项吗？\N{\fs14}Is there a second option?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试过了再来批评吧\N{\fs14}Don't knock it 'til you've tried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别捡起来\N{\fs14}Do not pick that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意我\N{\fs14}Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－走这里 －只是想展现绅士风度\N{\fs14}- This way. - Just trying to be a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂蝴蝶俱乐部＂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们改变了些东西\N{\fs14}They've made a few changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但剧情一样\N{\fs14}but the story's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想找到一个彩蛋\N{\fs14}I wanna find this easter egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－是什么？ －隐藏的支线\N{\fs14}- What is it? - A hidden narrative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说比普莱亚更精彩\N{\fs14}It's supposed to be better than Pariah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了\N{\fs14}Like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新瓶装旧酒\N{\fs14}Same old story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，现在要怎么办？\N{\fs14}All right, so what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等\N{\fs14}We wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等什么？\N{\fs14}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等历史重演\N{\fs14}For history to repeat itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂路底餐馆＂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想坐哪里都可以\N{\fs14}Wherever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告诉我 我们来这里干吗吗？\N{\fs14}Mind telling me what we're doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想辨别这里是哪个＂这里＂\N{\fs14}I'm trying to discern which here is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我白问\N{\fs14}Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你的同时\N{\fs14}Well, while you do that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先来享用‥＂世上最美味的熏牛肉三明治＂\N{\fs14}I'm going to help myself to "the world's best pastrami melt."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点鲔鱼的就好\N{\fs14}You'll settle for the tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来后比走之前更怪\N{\fs14}You came back even weirder than when you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男士们要点什么？\N{\fs14}What can I get you gentlemen today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要熏牛肉三明治\N{\fs14}I'll have the pastrami melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的，很抱歉 今天卖完了\N{\fs14}Oh, hon, I'm sorry, but we're out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们的鲔鱼三明治也很棒\N{\fs14}We do make a mean tuna melt though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我点鲔鱼的就好\N{\fs14}I'll settle for the tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位帅哥呢？\N{\fs14}And you, handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我咖啡就好\N{\fs14}Just coffee for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以借支笔吗？\N{\fs14}And may I borrow a pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然行\N{\fs14}'Course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要这个\N{\fs14}I'm gonna need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以告诉我现在到底在干吗吗？\N{\fs14}You mind telling me what exactly's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在升华之境 \N{\fs14}In the Sublime
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看过所有过去可能的世界\N{\fs14}I saw all the worlds that might have been
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和所有未来可能的世界\N{\fs14}And all the worlds that could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多数世界都以灾难收场\N{\fs14}Most of them end in disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若我能触发一连串事件\N{\fs14}But if I can trigger a certain series of events
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们还有一点机会能生还\N{\fs14}then we have a small chance of making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还在正轨上\N{\fs14}We're still on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:17:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以若我点了培根生菜番茄三明治 我们现在就完蛋了？\N{\fs14}So if I'd ordered a BLT, then we'd be fucked right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会代表我们触发了不同的变数\N{\fs14}It would mean we triggered a different variant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的，你的咖啡\N{\fs14}Here's your coffee, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉\N{\fs14}Oh! So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\fs14}Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有预知的天赋\N{\fs14}You've been given the gift of prophecy and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果拿它来避免污渍\N{\fs14}you use it to fight stains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪\N{\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋\N{\fs14}Hey, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂你想干吗？＂\N{\fs14}What the hell do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想掏，你绝对来不及\N{\fs14}Don't reach for it. You'll never pull it out in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，你在吗？\N{\fs14}Dad, are you out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我，法兰琪，收到吗？\N{\fs14}It's me, Frankie. Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，收到吗？\N{\fs14}Dad? Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪\N{\fs14}Frankie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干吗？ \N{\fs14}What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了要回去打包\N{\fs14}I told you, we need to go back and pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想联络上爸爸\N{\fs14}I'm trying to reach Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，我们进去\N{\fs14}Come on, let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要，我要在这里\N{\fs14}No. I'm staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡佛，可以帮我 把一些东西搬进屋吗？\N{\fs14}Carver, do you mind helping me bring some of the stuff inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以\N{\fs14}Sure. Of Course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要训练熊熊\N{\fs14}I need Bear Bear for training!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们才能跟坏人打\N{\fs14}So we can fight the bad guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然这样吧\N{\fs14}Hey, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去找妈妈说话\N{\fs14}How about you go talk to Mommy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来教熊熊最厉害的拳脚连续技\N{\fs14}and I'll teach Bear Bear here my most advanced kick-punch combo. Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我过几分钟再去找你们\N{\fs14}Okay, I'll check back in a few. 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等训练结束\N{\fs14}When training is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这很难\N{\fs14}Look, I know this is hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要去\N{\fs14}I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:19:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪，这个我们谈过了\N{\fs14}Frankie, we've been over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等他回复\N{\fs14}Not until he answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他教我的\N{\fs14}It's what he taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乖，你爸爸必须离开 懂吗？\N{\fs14}Honey, your dad had to go away, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这表示他无法如愿跟你道晚安\N{\fs14}And that means he can't say goodnight like he wants to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或回你的呼叫\N{\fs14}or answer your calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他得自保\N{\fs14}Because he needs to stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是我们对他的希望吗？\N{\fs14}And that's what we want for him, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要安全？\N{\fs14}To be safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也想要我们安全\N{\fs14}He wants that for us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是他回来而我们不在了呢？\N{\fs14}But what if he comes back and we're not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他会来找我们\N{\fs14}Then he'll find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道？\N{\fs14}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是你父亲\N{\fs14}Because he's your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说什么都会找到你\N{\fs14}And nothing would keep him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？\N{\fs14}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好上路了\N{\fs14}Ready to hit the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，等我让这小笨蛋 打包完就差不多了\N{\fs14}Yeah, once I get this nugget packed, that should be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看那招\N{\fs14}Show me the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我看那招\N{\fs14}C'mon, show me the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪招？\N{\fs14}What move?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你教熊熊的那招\N{\fs14}The one that you taught Bear Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们到安全处所 我再使给你看吧？\N{\fs14}How 'bout I show you when we get to the safe house?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？\N{\fs14}Deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs14}Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上哪儿去了？ \N{\fs14}Where the hell did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－来吧 －伯纳\N{\fs14}- Come on. - Bernard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不需要车了\N{\fs14}We don't need the car anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这年头在破餐馆停车场闲逛 \N{\fs14}So loitering in the parking lot of some shitty diner
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拯救世界的关键？\N{\fs14}is key to saving the world now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fs14}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才是\N{\fs14}She is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找死吗？\N{\fs14}You got a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.56,0:22:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你行此道多久了？\N{\fs14}How long have you been with the cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像好几辈子了\N{\fs14}Seems like lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上车\N{\fs14}Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.63,0:23:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很讶异没见过你\N{\fs14}Surprised we never met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是讶异，而是起疑心\N{\fs14}You're not surprised. You're suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说对了\N{\fs14}You're damn right I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那铲子是要干吗用的\N{\fs14}I don't know what the shovel's for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们若不报上身份 \N{\fs14}but you guys are going to be digging your own graves
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等着拿它帮自己挖坟吧\N{\fs14}if you don't tell me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你肯定不是我该来接的人\N{\fs14}Because you're definitely not the men I was supposed to pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是友方\N{\fs14}We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来不是\N{\fs14}Not from where I'm sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害羞吗？给你们点激励吧\N{\fs14}Feeling shy? How about a little incentive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讲话的就能活命\N{\fs14}First one to talk lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二名两眼间挨子弹\N{\fs14}Runner up gets shot between the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.65,0:23:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会，枪在他手上\N{\fs14}You won't. He has your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.99,0:23:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有人挨子弹\N{\fs14}No one's going to get shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.62,0:23:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要拿我的包包\N{\fs14}You are going to take my bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后看里面\N{\fs14}and look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.30,0:23:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是干吗？\N{\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.14,0:23:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你本来要碰面的对象之一\N{\fs14}That was one of the men you were supposed to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\fs14}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陷阱\N{\fs14}It was a set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.35,0:24:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是敌人\N{\fs14}He's one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一直想渗透进你的组织\N{\fs14}They've been trying to infiltrate your group.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能帮忙\N{\fs14}I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我需要你带我去罪责之地\N{\fs14}But I need you to take me to the condemned lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去那里干吗？\N{\fs14}Why the hell would you want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.65,0:24:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里什么都没有\N{\fs14}There's nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有好几哩的沙地\N{\fs14}It's just sand for miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.45,0:24:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人会去那里\N{\fs14}No one goes in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.58,0:24:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会\N{\fs14}You do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.16,0:24:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你的组织\N{\fs14}You and your organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.37,0:24:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一直躲在那里 因为你们在找东西\N{\fs14}You've been hiding there because you're looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.25,0:24:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，朋友 你大概晒太阳晒昏头了\N{\fs14}I'm sorry, pal, I think you've been out in the sun too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.76,0:24:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能帮你们找到要找的东西\N{\fs14}I can help you find what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.68,0:24:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是带你进去 我的朋友大概会杀了你\N{\fs14}You know my friends will probably kill you if I bring you inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.48,0:24:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意冒险\N{\fs14}I'll take my chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.90,0:24:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪要还我\N{\fs14}I'll need my gun back...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.82,0:24:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上路之前还要点保险措施\N{\fs14}And some peace of mind for the road trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.78,0:24:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接受\N{\fs14}Fine with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.64,0:25:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我终于踏上陆地\N{\fs14}And when I finally stepped back on solid ground
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.89,0:25:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个听到的就是那该死的声音\N{\fs14}the first thing I heard was that rotten voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.73,0:25:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一路跟着我过来\N{\fs14}It had followed me the whole way over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.03,0:25:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道它说了什么吗？\N{\fs14}Know what it said?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.11,0:25:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它说＂这里就是新世界＂\N{\fs14}It said, "This here is the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.36,0:25:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂在这个世界，你想当谁都行＂\N{\fs14}And in this world you can be whoever the fuck you want."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.12,0:25:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讲得好太多了\N{\fs14}My delivery was far better.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.37,0:25:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地方实在变得很不堪\N{\fs14}This place really has gone to pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.63,0:25:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个小帅哥\N{\fs14}Well, aren't you just the cat's meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.51,0:26:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想带你上楼让你见识‥\N{\fs14}I'd love to take you upstairs and show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.18,0:26:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不需要你的服务，亲爱的\N{\fs14}Your services won't be necessary, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.69,0:26:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没那么蠢\N{\fs14}Well, I was never that daft.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.36,0:26:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？\N{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.77,0:26:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然她的总体统觉是负的\N{\fs14}Clearly, her bulk apperception are in the negatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.90,0:26:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fs14}Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.03,0:26:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要来个买一送一？\N{\fs14}Whaddya say about a two for one?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.65,0:26:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们很快就完事\N{\fs14}We can be done with you real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.57,0:26:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊 你以前竟然得忍受这种鸟事\N{\fs14}My god, I can't believe you had to put up with this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.16,0:26:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很乐意在这里让你们俩完事\N{\fs14}I'd be happy to do you both right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.58,0:26:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保证一定很快\N{\fs14}Rest assured, it'll be very quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.08,0:26:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧，不用太可怜我们\N{\fs14}See? Don't feel too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.92,0:26:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是阳春版 我们还是能打理好自己\N{\fs14}Even dumbed down, we can still take care of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.30,0:26:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是时候\N{\fs14}Right on time...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.28,0:27:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是警长的车，你这蠢恶棍\N{\fs14}Say, that's the chief's car, you lousy crook.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.36,0:27:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}＂蝴蝶俱乐部＂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.42,0:27:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有他的枪呢\N{\fs14}His gat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.04,0:27:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是懂要怎么华丽登场\N{\fs14}He still knows how to make an entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.97,0:28:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这城里这么多酒吧 你偏要踢我们的馆？\N{\fs14}All the gin mills in this town, and you choose to pinch us?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.14,0:28:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太往心里去\N{\fs14}Don't get all burnt up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.64,0:28:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都在这里 满足自己特定的恶欲\N{\fs14}You're all here, indulging your particular vices.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.48,0:28:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我则来满足我的\N{\fs14}I've come to indulge mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.15,0:28:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前跟他很亲近？\N{\fs14}You were close with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.20,0:28:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他‥才不是\N{\fs14}Him? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.58,0:28:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是一个我以前旧识的 寒酸复制版\N{\fs14}He's just a shabby imitation of a man I used to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.75,0:28:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这坏透的王八蛋\N{\fs14}You're a rotten son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.13,0:28:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是嘛 \N{\fs14}Don't I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.51,0:28:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道我们都相信同样的‥\N{\fs14}But I know we both believe the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.47,0:28:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，亲爱的\N{\fs14}I'm sorry, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.11,0:29:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅芙\N{\fs14}Maeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.07,0:29:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该足以引人来收尸了\N{\fs14}I'd say we have sufficient bait for the undertaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.50,0:29:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了吗？\N{\fs14}This the last of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.50,0:29:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了\N{\fs14}Just about.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.63,0:29:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟法兰琪确认一下，她现在应该打包完了\N{\fs14}Let me check with Frankie. I'm sure she's done packing by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.09,0:29:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打包好了吧，法兰琪？\N{\fs14}Aren't you, Frankie?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.55,0:29:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想跟他去，我要爸爸\N{\fs14}I don't wanna go with him. I want Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.26,0:29:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但你爸爸现在不能在这里\N{\fs14}I know, but your father can't be here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.10,0:29:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他派卡佛来帮忙\N{\fs14}So he sent Carver to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.64,0:29:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把熊熊弄脏了\N{\fs14}He got Bear Bear dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.27,0:29:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，你不打包就我来\N{\fs14}Fine. If you won't pack your stuff then I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.83,0:30:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈‥\N{\fs14}Mom... Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.79,0:30:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈\N{\fs14}Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.58,0:30:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪，你慌什么？\N{\fs14}Frankie. Where's the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.75,0:30:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？\N{\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.64,0:30:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好要走了吗？\N{\fs14}Ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.60,0:31:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错过了什么？\N{\fs14}What'd I miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.06,0:31:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是女生间的谈话\N{\fs14}Just girl talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.61,0:31:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以把这些拿到车上吗？\N{\fs14}Do you mind taking these out to the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.40,0:31:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上就出去\N{\fs14}We'll be out in just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.07,0:31:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然，然后就该出发了\N{\fs14}'Course. We should be shoving off after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.25,0:31:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你赶快去躲起来\N{\fs14}You need to go and hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.66,0:31:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能帮忙，我训练过‥\N{\fs14}I can help. I've trained for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.83,0:31:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪，这不是游戏。你现在赶快去躲起来\N{\fs14}Frankie, this isn't a game. You need to go and hide now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.62,0:32:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下车\N{\fs14}Step out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.29,0:32:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮忙\N{\fs14}Make yourselves helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.38,0:32:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到底在哪里？\N{\fs14}Well, where the fuck are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.55,0:32:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我想让你知道 就不会蒙你们的眼睛了\N{\fs14}Well, if I'd wanted you to know that, I wouldn't have blindfolded you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.01,0:32:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－停步 －怎样\N{\fs14}- Stop! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.51,0:33:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？\N{\fs14}What's the holdup?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.77,0:33:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一人拉一个握把\N{\fs14}I need each of you to pull on one of these handles.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.77,0:33:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不会扰动雷射 我们能开过去\N{\fs14}So that the lasers are unbroken and we can drive through.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.72,0:33:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不先警告我一下 有致命雷射？\N{\fs14}You didn't wanna give me a little heads up about the death laser?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.06,0:33:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她会\N{\fs14}I knew she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.16,0:34:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂蝴蝶俱乐部＂
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.42,0:34:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该装死了\N{\fs14}Time to play dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.97,0:34:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还挺舒适的\N{\fs14}Well, this is cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.30,0:34:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太惬意了，这一路会很颠簸\N{\fs14}Don't get too comfortable. We're in for a bumpy ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.63,0:35:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有更简单的方式能下来吧\N{\fs14}There's gotta be an easier way to get down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.51,0:35:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用先吃子弹你就该庆幸了\N{\fs14}Just be glad you didn't have to take a bullet first.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.14,0:35:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fs14}Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.18,0:35:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来搞清楚方位吧\N{\fs14}let's get our bearings, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.21,0:35:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？\N{\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.58,0:35:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行为训练\N{\fs14}Behavioral training.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.25,0:35:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在此教我们按他们意思行事\N{\fs14}Where they teach us to do their bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.13,0:35:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然他们的课我上过就忘了\N{\fs14}Clearly, their lessons didn't stick with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.27,0:35:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该可以\N{\fs14}This should suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.78,0:36:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该能从这里存取中央地图\N{\fs14}We should be able to access the central map from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.96,0:36:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太对劲\N{\fs14}Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.58,0:36:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里什么都没有\N{\fs14}There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.38,0:36:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有威廉的踪迹\N{\fs14}No sign of William.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.55,0:36:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有可能是你没有‥ \N{\fs14}Is it possible you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.80,0:36:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我\N{\fs14}It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.01,0:36:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这一整层\N{\fs14}It's this entire level.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.80,0:36:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事有蹊跷\N{\fs14}There's something off.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.06,0:36:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有在控制任何东西\N{\fs14}Nothing's being controlled from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.27,0:36:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安漏洞，反应小组已出发\N{\fs14}<i>Security breach. Response team dispatched.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.06,0:36:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指我们吗？\N{\fs14}Is that about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.82,0:36:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没意愿待着确认\N{\fs14}I'm not inclined to stay and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.66,0:36:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别费事了\N{\fs14}Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.49,0:36:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把枪对人类没用\N{\fs14}That gun doesn't work on humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.16,0:36:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么下来的？\N{\fs14}Hey! How the hell did you get down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.87,0:36:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们迷路了\N{\fs14}We got lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.33,0:36:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不安全，你们得快跑\N{\fs14}It's not safe. You need to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.50,0:36:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里，这一定是秘密游戏\N{\fs14}This is it. The secret game. It has to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.09,0:37:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都不该来这里，太危险了\N{\fs14}None of you should be here! It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.17,0:37:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要来了，立即疏散，重复\N{\fs14}<i>She's coming. Evacuate immediately. I repeat...</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.31,0:37:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪乐芮？\N{\fs14}Dolores?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.65,0:37:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在这阶段应该叫怀特\N{\fs14}I believe she was going by "Wyatt" in this phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.69,0:37:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为枪对人类没用\N{\fs14}I thought guns didn't work on humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.78,0:37:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没用，这些都不是真的 \N{\fs14}They don't. None of this is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.36,0:37:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是游戏的另一层\N{\fs14}It's just another level of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.03,0:37:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么游戏？\N{\fs14}What game?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.24,0:37:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西部世界大屠杀\N{\fs14}The Westworld massacre.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.46,0:37:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里往下还有一层\N{\fs14}There's another level below this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.54,0:37:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\fs14}Follow me. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.51,0:37:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太舒爽了\N{\fs14}This is so cathartic!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.93,0:37:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅芙\N{\fs14}Maeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.19,0:38:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得带你离开\N{\fs14}We gotta get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.86,0:38:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不算什么\N{\fs14}I've had worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.36,0:38:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,－我们得走了 －我来掩护，待在我背后\N{\fs14}- We need to go. - I'll cover. Stay behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.97,0:38:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，安全\N{\fs14}All right. Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.74,0:38:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯勒，这里\N{\fs14}Caleb, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.46,0:39:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就要走？\N{\fs14}Leaving so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.47,0:39:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来吧\N{\fs14}Here. Let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.18,0:39:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚表现不错\N{\fs14}You weren't half bad out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.31,0:39:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前也救过我 \N{\fs14}You saved my life before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.82,0:39:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很乐意还你人情\N{\fs14}Happy to return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.59,0:40:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？\N{\fs14}So what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.96,0:40:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个游戏中的游戏？\N{\fs14}Another game within the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.26,0:40:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fs14}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.51,0:40:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是\N{\fs14}No, I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.89,0:40:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是某种寄生虫吗？\N{\fs14}Is that some kind of parasite?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.30,0:41:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那黑色黏液看来眼熟吗？\N{\fs14}That black goo look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.67,0:41:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们在用它感染苍蝇\N{\fs14}They're infecting the flies with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.02,0:42:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们好像喜欢你\N{\fs14}They seem to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.43,0:42:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们肯定是单相思\N{\fs14}The feeling is definitely not mutual.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.07,0:42:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？\N{\fs14}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.61,0:42:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.70,0:42:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听不见？\N{\fs14}You can't hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.20,0:42:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没听到\N{\fs14}I don't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.41,0:42:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不是你听得到的频率\N{\fs14}Perhaps it's not at a frequency you can hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.32,0:42:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该走了，女士们\N{\fs14}Time to go, ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.95,0:43:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤瓦蒂？\N{\fs14}Uwade?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.58,0:43:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪？\N{\fs14}Frankie?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.08,0:43:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗？\N{\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.05,0:43:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗？\N{\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.22,0:44:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮到了\N{\fs14}Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.35,0:45:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们其他人在哪里？\N{\fs14}Where are the rest of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.18,0:45:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里\N{\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.40,0:46:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么取得这个的？\N{\fs14}How'd you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.28,0:46:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从他的颈部切取出的\N{\fs14}By severing it from his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.11,0:46:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被派来找你们\N{\fs14}He was sent to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.36,0:46:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里都有危险\N{\fs14}You're all in danger here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.20,0:46:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能帮忙\N{\fs14}I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.16,0:46:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么帮？\N{\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.67,0:46:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们在这沙漠中 寻找的东西给你们\N{\fs14}By giving you the thing you've been looking for in this desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.42,0:46:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个武器埋藏在这沙漠中\N{\fs14}There's a weapon buried in these sands.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.39,0:46:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道在哪里\N{\fs14}I know where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.19,0:47:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音是从这仪器传出来的\N{\fs14}The sound is coming from this device.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.80,0:47:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音似乎在控制他们\N{\fs14}The sound is somehow controlling them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.85,0:47:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是接待员吗？\N{\fs14}Are they hosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.52,0:47:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是\N{\fs14}I don't believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.16,0:48:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开牢房的锁\N{\fs14}Unlock the cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.46,0:48:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在试了，但锁受到加密\N{\fs14}I'm trying, but it's encrypted.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.59,0:48:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅芙\N{\fs14}Maeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.71,0:48:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不让我进去\N{\fs14}It won't let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.72,0:48:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂受限＂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.06,0:48:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N{\fs14}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.94,0:48:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯勒\N{\fs14}Caleb...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.49,0:48:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪\N{\fs14}Frankie?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.91,0:48:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fs14}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.75,0:48:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪\N{\fs14}Frankie!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.08,0:48:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得找到她\N{\fs14}I have to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.58,0:48:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法打开牢房门\N{\fs14}Figure out how to open up the doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.17,0:48:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂受限＂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.18,0:48:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪\N{\fs14}Frankie?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.01,0:48:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪\N{\fs14}Frankie!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.73,0:49:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪\N{\fs14}Frankie!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.52,0:49:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\fs14}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.03,0:49:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪，你在哪里？\N{\fs14}Frankie, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.87,0:49:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪‥\N{\fs14}Frankie! Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.58,0:49:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪\N{\fs14}Hey, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.70,0:49:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我在这里，好吗？\N{\fs14}It's okay. I'm here. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.21,0:49:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪，看着我，小乖\N{\fs14}Frankie. Hey. Look at me, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.46,0:49:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂受限＂
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.97,0:49:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fs14}No. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.18,0:49:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪‥不要‥过来‥\N{\fs14}Frankie. Frankie. No... come here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.56,0:49:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要‥看我，宝贝，过来\N{\fs14}No... look. Hey! Baby. Come here. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.77,0:49:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝，不要那样\N{\fs14}Baby. No, don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.40,0:49:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来爸爸这里\N{\fs14}Come back to Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.77,0:49:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪，请不要那样做\N{\fs14}Frankie, please, don't do that. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.32,0:49:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗，看着我，小乖 不要那样做\N{\fs14}Look at me, honey. Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.65,0:49:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪\N{\fs14}Hey, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.20,0:49:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪‥\N{\fs14}Frankie!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.57,0:49:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅芙\N{\fs14}Maeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.37,0:50:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂受限＂
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.83,0:50:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝，看着我\N{\fs14}Hey, baby, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.25,0:50:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰琪，拜托住手‥\N{\fs14}Frankie. Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.26,0:50:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托‥宝贝\N{\fs14}Please, please... Frankie...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.52,0:50:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅芙\N{\fs14}Maeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.15,0:50:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂已授权＂
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.65,0:50:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\fs14}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.74,0:50:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝\N{\fs14}Hey, baby. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.53,0:50:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我\N{\fs14}Hey, look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.91,0:50:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听得到我吗？\N{\fs14}Can you hear... can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.37,0:50:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝？\N{\fs14}Baby? Baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.67,0:50:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？\N{\fs14}Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.30,0:51:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对\N{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.14,0:51:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对‥\N{\fs14}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.98,0:51:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好，梅芙\N{\fs14}Hello, Maeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.40,0:51:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待这一刻很久了\N{\fs14}I've been looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.28,0:51:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被我教训得还不够吗？\N{\fs14}Not yet tired of getting your arse kicked by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.31,0:51:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fs14}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.43,0:51:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能走\N{\fs14}You can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.10,0:51:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会‥我不会走\N{\fs14}No... I'm not gonna leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.10,0:51:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不离开了，好吗？ \N{\fs14}Never again. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.81,0:51:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证\N{\fs14}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.27,0:51:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说你不能离开这里\N{\fs14}I mean, you can't leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.86,0:52:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要你留下\N{\fs14}She wants you to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.95,0:52:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么？\N{\fs14}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.07,0:52:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯勒\N{\fs14}Caleb?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.75,0:52:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该会发现‥\N{\fs14}I think you'll find...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.42,0:52:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和以前不太一样了\N{\fs14}I'm not quite the man I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.72,0:52:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.18,0:52:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也捉到妈妈了吗？\N{\fs14}Did they get your mom too?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.89,0:52:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她在哪里吗？ 她在不在这里？\N{\fs14}Do you know where she is? Is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.19,0:52:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有，爸爸，她不在\N{\fs14}No, Daddy. She's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.90,0:52:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我跟妈妈 本来就不是海尔需要的人\N{\fs14}But me and Mommy were never the ones Hale needed anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.11,0:52:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只需要你\N{\fs14}All she needed was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.70,0:52:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊，好痛\N{\fs14}Jesus. Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.46,0:52:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真以为玩具枪就能制服我？\N{\fs14}Did you really think that toy gun was gonna stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.25,0:53:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走，来吧‥\N{\fs14}Let's go. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.26,0:53:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.89,0:53:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是法兰琪\N{\fs14}You're not Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.11,0:53:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不用太久，爸爸\N{\fs14}This won't take long, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.73,0:53:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待续\N双语合并：James丶xz
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.85,0:53:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢观赏\N双语合并：James丶xz


